{"lemma":"حَسْرَةُ","slug":"حَسْرَةُ","root":"ح.س.ر","root_slug":"ح-س-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-س-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"حَسْرَة","root":"حسر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":7},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n7967","n7972"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%B3%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"regret, sorrow"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pity","examples":[{"text":"يَا حَسْرَةً عَلَى الْعِبَادِ مَا يَأْتِيهِم مِن رَسُولٍ إِلَّا كَانُوا بِهِ يَسْتَهْزِئُونَ","english":"Oh pity on such beings! Never has a messenger come to them except that they derided him"}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ħas.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7967","headword_ar":"حَسَرَهُ","root":"Hsr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HasorN","text_ar":"حَسْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HusuwrN","text_ar":"حُسُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He removed it, put it off, took it off,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stripped if off,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano $aYo'K","text_ar":"عَنْ شَىْءٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from a thing which it covered"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"concealed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Husira","text_ar":"حُسِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said of anything as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was removed, put off, taken off,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stripped off,"},{"kind":"text","text":"from a thing which it covered or concealed. (A.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasara kum~ahu Eano *iraAEihi","text_ar":"حَسَرَ كُمَّهُ عَنْ ذِرَاعِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He removed his sleeve from his fore arm."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A.) And simply"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasara Eano *iraAEihi","text_ar":"حَسَرَ عَنْ ذِرَاعِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He uncovered his fore arm."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasara EimaAmatahu Eano raA^osihi","text_ar":"حَسَرَ عِمَامَتَهُ عَنْ رَاْسِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He removed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took off, his turban from his head."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasarato diroEahaA","text_ar":"حَسَرَتْ دِرْعَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a woman)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took off her shift"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, Msb)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano jasadihaA","text_ar":"عَنْ جَسَدِهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from her body:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ximaArahaA","text_ar":"خِمَارَهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"her head-covering."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasarati Alr~iyHu","text_ar":"حَسَرَتِ الرِّيحُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~aHaAba","text_ar":"السَّحَابَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The wind removed the clouds"},{"kind":"text","text":"from the"},{"kind":"page_break","n":568},{"kind":"text","text":"sky]. (A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasara qinaAEa Alham~i Ean~iY","text_ar":"حَسَرَ قِنَاعَ الهَمِّ عَنِّى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, removed the covering of anxiety from me"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b3-  Also, (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HasorN","text_ar":"حَسْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He peeled"},{"kind":"text","text":"a branch of a tree. (K, TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He swept"},{"kind":"text","text":"a house or chamber. (K, TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasaruwhu","text_ar":"حَسَرُوهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HasorN","text_ar":"حَسْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HusorN","text_ar":"حُسْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They begged of him and he gave them until nothing remained in his possession."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasara","text_ar":"حَسَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HasorN","text_ar":"حَسْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HusuwrN","text_ar":"حُسُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AHsr","text_ar":"احسر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iHosaArN","text_ar":"اـِحْسَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hs~r","text_ar":"حسّر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHosiyrN","text_ar":"تَحْسِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man, S, A,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a journey, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tired, fatigued,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"jaded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K,) a beast, (A, TA,) or a camel: (S:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he drove"},{"kind":"text","text":"a camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"until he tired, fatigued,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"jaded, him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Husirati Ald~aAb~apu","text_ar":"حُسِرَتِ الدَّابَّةُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The beast was fatigued so that it was left to remain where it was."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHeyth.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasara","text_ar":"حَسَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the distance to which it looked, and the indistinctness of the object,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fatigued"},{"kind":"text","text":"the eye. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Husira AlbaSaru mino Tuwli Aln~aZari","text_ar":"حُسِرَ البَصَرُ مِنْ طُولِ النَّظَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The eye was fatigued by the length of looking:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see a similar meaning of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasara","text_ar":"حَسَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasira","text_ar":"حَسِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below]. (A.)       -A3-  See 7, with which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasara","text_ar":"حَسَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is syn. ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasara","text_ar":"حَسَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (ISk, A, Mgh, Msb,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(water)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sank and disappeared;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became low;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retired:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISk, A, Mgh:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it sank and disappeared,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retired, from its place:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) properly,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it became removed from the shore:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the sea, or great river,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sank,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retired,"},{"kind":"text","text":"from ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano","text_ar":"عَنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":") El-'Irák, and from the shore,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that the ground which was beneath the water appeared:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) you do not say, in this sense, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AnHsr","text_ar":"انحسر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Az. [But this latter is sometimes used, as, for instance, in the Msb art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jzr","text_ar":"جزر"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) Hence, in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kulo maA Hasara Eanohu AlbaHoru","text_ar":"كُلْ مَا حَسَرَ عَنْهُ البَحْرُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wadaEo maA TafaA Ealayohi","text_ar":"وَدَعْ مَا طَفَا عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Eat thou that from which the sea retires, and leave what floats upon it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasara","text_ar":"حَسَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HusuwrN","text_ar":"حُسُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasara","text_ar":"حَسَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasra","text_ar":"حَسرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HasarN","text_ar":"حَسَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstHsr","text_ar":"استحسر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tHs~r","text_ar":"تحسّر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel, S, or a beast, A)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became tired, fatigued,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"jaded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by travel:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [or] the last signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fell down from fatigue."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 491.) [Hence,] it is said in a trad., ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AudoEuwA A@ll~`ha wa laA tasotaHosiruwA","text_ar":"اُدْعُوا ا@للّٰهَ وَ لَا تَسْتَحْسِرُوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Supplicate ye God, and be not weary:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and a similar instance occurs in the Kur xxi. 19. (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasara","text_ar":"حَسَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) or"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HusuwrN","text_ar":"حُسُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, Msb, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasira","text_ar":"حَسِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (A;) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the sight)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, dim, dull,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hebetated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it failed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became fatigued;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] by reason of length of space [overlooked], (S, Msb, K,) and the like; (S, Msb;) or by long looking. (A.)       -A5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasira Ealayohi","text_ar":"حَسِرَ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HasarN","text_ar":"حَسَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HasorapN","text_ar":"حَسْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) or the latter is a simple subst., (Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HasaraAnN","text_ar":"حَسَرَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He grieved for it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regretted it; he felt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"expressed, grief, sorrow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regret, on account of it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"talah~afa","text_ar":"تَلَهَّفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Msb, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tHs~r","text_ar":"تحسّر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) or the former,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he grieved for it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regretted it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"talah~afa Ealayohi","text_ar":"تَلَهَّفَ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", S, A, or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nadima Ealayohi","text_ar":"نَدِمَ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA,) namely, a thing that had escaped him,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most intensely."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, * TA.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HasorapN","text_ar":"حَسْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","Mgh","TA","A","ISk"]},{"entry_id":"n7972","headword_ar":"حَسْرَةٌ","root":"Hsr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Grief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regret;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"talah~ufN","text_ar":"تَلَهُّفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taA^as~ufN","text_ar":"تَاَسُّفٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nadaAmapN","text_ar":"نَدَامَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Jel in ii. 162 and viii. 36 and xxxix. 57,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nadamN","text_ar":"نَدَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gam~N","text_ar":"غَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Bd in viii. 36:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intense lamentation"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"expression of pain"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of grief"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of sorrow;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$id~apu Alt~aA^al~umi","text_ar":"شِدَّةُ التَّاَلُّمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Jel in vi. 31 and xxxvi. 29:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most intense grief"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regret"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$ad~u Alt~alah~ufi","text_ar":"اَشَدُّ التَّلَهُّفِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", S, or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$ad~u Aln~adami","text_ar":"اَشَدُّ النَّدَمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", Zj)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for a thing that has escaped one,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S,) so that he who feels it is like a beast that is tired, or fatigued, or jaded, ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hasiyr","text_ar":"حَسِير"},{"kind":"text","text":",) and of no use: (Zj in xxxvi. 29 of the Kur:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HasaraAtN","text_ar":"حَسَرَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaA HasorataA Ealayohi","text_ar":"يَا حَسْرَتَا عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O my grief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regret,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for it!"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (A.)"}],"source_refs":["Msb","K","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}